      "名称": "unifiedDataChannel",
      "所属模块": "@kit.ArkData",
      "功能描述": "As a part of the Unified Data Management Framework (UDMF), the unifiedDataChannel module provides unified data channels and standard data access interfaces for many-to-many data sharing across applications. It also provides definitions for uniform data types, such as text and image, to streamline data interaction between different applications and minimize the workload of data type adaptation. Although the UDMF does not parse user data, you are advised not to transfer sensitive personal data or privacy data due to low-level security of storage path.",
